I"
	<p>寒假期间完成的SD卡SDIO模式驱动以及FATFS文件系统移植当时测试没有问题，昨天跟今天搞了搞开发板上LCD显示汉字的程序，参考例程为原子战舰V3的汉字显示实验。</p>

<h2 id="具体问题">具体问题</h2>

<p>1、当使用</p>
<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-c" data-lang="c"> <span class="n">strcpy</span><span class="p">((</span><span class="n">char_</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">pname</span><span class="p">,(</span><span class="n">char_</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">src</span><span class="p">);</span> <span class="n">strcat</span><span class="p">((</span><span class="n">char_</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">pname</span><span class="p">,(</span><span class="n">char_</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">UNIGBK_PATH</span><span class="p">);</span> <span class="n">res</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">update_fontx</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">20</span><span class="n">_size</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">y</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">size</span><span class="p">,(</span><span class="k">const</span> <span class="n">TCHAR_</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">pname</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">);</span> </code></pre></figure>
<p><br />
读取字库文件时出现<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">f_open</code>无法读取文件的情况，当把<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pname</code>直接写成<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">0:/SYSTEM/FONT/UNIGBK.BIN</code> 时读取正常。<br />
2、在从SD卡读取数据写入到W25Q64时出现了不能连续读取SD卡数据的情况，拔出SD卡重新插入有一定几率恢复继续写入，如此反复写入完成后，后续程序可顺利运行。</p>

<h2 id="解决方法">解决方法</h2>

<p>问题1暂时可用上面的解决方法解决。<br />
问题2没有查到有效解决方法，留作存档。</p>

